{"title":"樱与松——送华国锋同志访日","authors":["阮章竞"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":5,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"樱与松"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——送华国锋同志访日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阮章竞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日本的樱花中国的松，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同种一园迎春风；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"根相交，枝相连，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同生共长阳光中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日本的樱花中国的松，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同度炎暑傲霜雪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送冬去，迎春来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年同迎樱花节。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花似朝霞松更绿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔海同欢度节日。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"樱与松，松与樱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天长地久相扶持。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}